<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 22:06:47 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>本-格维尔呼吁未经认证的女兵处理枪支许可证的发放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-calls-on-uncertified-national-service-women-to-handle-gun-permits-issuing/0000018c-5ed1-dbd5-a39c-fff38cb00000</link><description>本-格维尔在获得法律批准之前就批准了该职位的广告，消息人士称，这位极右翼部长这样做是为了获得政治分数。执照办事员应该仔细审查申请人，确保他们符合拥有枪支的心理和身体健康要求</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 21:05:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-calls-on-uncertified-national-service-women-to-handle-gun-permits-issuing/0000018c-5ed1-dbd5-a39c-fff38cb00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警察局长任命本-格维尔高级职员加入西岸警察</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-police-chief-appoints-a-senior-member-of-ben-gvirs-office-to-west-bank-police/0000018c-5da3-d6f9-afbc-5deb5d810000</link><description>消息人士称，更适合该职位的候选人被拒绝，其中一位消息人士称，本-格维尔“想指派一名自己的人”到以色列最敏感的警察区之一</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 20:09:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-police-chief-appoints-a-senior-member-of-ben-gvirs-office-to-west-bank-police/0000018c-5da3-d6f9-afbc-5deb5d810000</guid></item><item><title>以色列正处于战争状态，内塔尼亚胡刚刚发起连任竞选</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-at-war-and-netanyahu-just-launched-his-re-election-campaign/0000018c-5f3f-de43-affd-ff3ff7c60000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡在民意调查中严重落后，并且正处于加沙与哈马斯的血腥冲突之中，他希望将以色列人在 10 月 7 日之后的创伤和愤怒转化为自己的选举需求</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 19:43:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-at-war-and-netanyahu-just-launched-his-re-election-campaign/0000018c-5f3f-de43-affd-ff3ff7c60000</guid></item><item><title>拜登称以色列因加沙爆炸事件失去国际支持，内塔尼亚胡必须“改变”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/biden-says-israel-losing-support-over-gaza-bombings-netanyahu-must-change-his-government/0000018c-5f60-d798-adac-ffef14800000</link><description>美国总统表示，以色列不能对巴勒斯坦国说不，这进一步表明美国对以色列轰炸加沙的行为日益担忧。周二早些时候，内塔尼亚胡表示，以色列和美国在“哈马斯之后的第二天”计划存在分歧</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 19:36:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/biden-says-israel-losing-support-over-gaza-bombings-netanyahu-must-change-his-government/0000018c-5f60-d798-adac-ffef14800000</guid></item><item><title>忘记美国大学校长吧，我们应该担心他们的犹太学生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-12/ty-article/.highlight/forget-u-s-college-heads-we-should-worry-about-their-jewish-students/0000018c-5f6a-de43-affd-ff6ac27a0000</link><description>当暴力呼吁变成“行为”时，就为时已晚了。美国的犹太学生怎么能像这样生活，时刻关心自己的福祉呢？他们怎么能时刻保持警惕呢？</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 19:18:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-12/ty-article/.highlight/forget-u-s-college-heads-we-should-worry-about-their-jewish-students/0000018c-5f6a-de43-affd-ff6ac27a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方称13名在加沙被杀的士兵被误认为是哈马斯成员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-13-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-were-mistakenly-identified-as-hamas-members/0000018c-5e46-dbd5-a39c-ff770e560000</link><description>以色列军队补充说，另有七名士兵在战争期间的其他行动事故中丧生。自地面行动开始以来，迄今已有105名士兵在加沙丧生</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 16:07:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-13-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-were-mistakenly-identified-as-hamas-members/0000018c-5e46-dbd5-a39c-ff770e560000</guid></item><item><title>考古学家对将圣经中的耶路撒冷一分为二的巨大护城河感到困惑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-12-12/ty-article/archaeologists-bewildered-by-monumental-moat-that-split-biblical-jerusalem-in-two/0000018c-5eac-d6f9-afbc-5feeab320000</link><description>以色列考古学家发现了一条刻在岩石上的巨大沟渠，这条沟渠可能在 3000 年前将古耶路撒冷一分为二，精英分子在一边，其余人在另一边。为什么是另一个问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 15:52:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-12-12/ty-article/archaeologists-bewildered-by-monumental-moat-that-split-biblical-jerusalem-in-two/0000018c-5eac-d6f9-afbc-5feeab320000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡办公室获得数百万美元资助以色列最新预算中的信息宣传活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-gets-millions-to-fund-info-campaigns-in-israels-updated-budget/0000018c-5e9b-dbd5-a39c-fffb6fcd0000</link><description>部分资金将流向一个拥有自己的广播团队的内部电视工作室，批评者称这将是国家控制的媒体，公共外交部已被解散</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 15:48:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-gets-millions-to-fund-info-campaigns-in-israels-updated-budget/0000018c-5e9b-dbd5-a39c-fffb6fcd0000</guid></item><item><title>犹太人和巴勒斯坦人都是西方种族主义的受害者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/jews-and-palestinians-are-both-victims-of-western-racism/0000018c-5e28-d6f9-afbc-5f6a74e10000</link><description>如今，和平的希望已成为过去。以色列与哈马斯战争的唯一赢家将是战争本身</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 15:04:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/jews-and-palestinians-are-both-victims-of-western-racism/0000018c-5e28-d6f9-afbc-5f6a74e10000</guid></item><item><title>“即使是所有以色列人质回家的照片也不会是胜利的形象”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/even-a-picture-of-all-the-hostages-returning-home-wouldnt-be-an-image-of-victory/0000018c-5d91-de43-affd-fd93d60e0000</link><description>当前的战争相当于 1967 年以色列伞兵在西墙充满敬畏的标志性照片吗？专家解释了为什么即使是哈马斯领导人叶海亚辛瓦尔尸体的照片也无法消除10月7日的恐怖画面所带来的失落感</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 14:58:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/even-a-picture-of-all-the-hostages-returning-home-wouldnt-be-an-image-of-victory/0000018c-5d91-de43-affd-fd93d60e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡称 10 月 7 日的《奥斯陆协议》受害者人数相同，引发愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-sparks-outrage-after-saying-october-7-oslo-accords-had-same-number-of-victims/0000018c-5e25-d6f9-afbc-5f6f9e160000</link><description>据希伯来媒体报道，以色列内塔尼亚胡在闭门会议上表示，1993 年和平协议签署后，在恐怖袭击中丧生的人数“与 10 月 7 日的受害者人数相同，但持续时间更长”</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 13:47:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-sparks-outrage-after-saying-october-7-oslo-accords-had-same-number-of-victims/0000018c-5e25-d6f9-afbc-5f6f9e160000</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装用突破性的伊朗导弹威胁红海航运</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-12/ty-article-magazine/houthis-threaten-red-sea-shipping-with-groundbreaking-iranian-missile/0000018c-5aa4-df2f-adac-feadd7220000</link><description>弹道导弹旨在攻击城市和战略设施等固定目标。中国和伊朗更进一步，开发能够击中移动船只的弹道导弹。过去几周，胡塞武装两次向货轮发射此类炮弹</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 13:36:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-12/ty-article-magazine/houthis-threaten-red-sea-shipping-with-groundbreaking-iranian-missile/0000018c-5aa4-df2f-adac-feadd7220000</guid></item><item><title>近东救济工程处如何成为继哈马斯之后加沙第二大有影响力的组织</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-unrwa-became-the-second-most-important-organization-in-gaza/0000018c-5deb-d798-adac-fdefaf450000</link><description>该联合国机构每年的预算超过 10 亿美元，控制着加沙地带一半以上的学校，并据报道与哈马斯有联系，批评者指责该联合国机构在巴以冲突中发挥着关键作用</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 13:18:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-unrwa-became-the-second-most-important-organization-in-gaza/0000018c-5deb-d798-adac-fdefaf450000</guid></item><item><title>红海岸线：也门胡塞武装袭击的所有船只</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-red-sea-front-all-ships-attacked-by-yemens-houthis/0000018c-5df7-d6f9-afbc-5dff7a430000</link><description>在伊朗的支持下，也门胡塞武装使用巡航导弹、无人机和反舰弹道导弹瞄准以色列拥有的船只或他们确定正在前往以色列的船只</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 13:16:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-red-sea-front-all-ships-attacked-by-yemens-houthis/0000018c-5df7-d6f9-afbc-5dff7a430000</guid></item><item><title>以色列精锐空军预备役军人表示，在内塔尼亚胡访问基地期间，他们被命令避开</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/reservists-in-elite-iaf-units-say-ordered-to-steer-clear-during-netanyahu-visit/0000018c-5de2-dbd5-a39c-fff308230000</link><description>Shaldag 和 669 精锐部队的预备役军人正在参加加沙地带的战斗，他们声称该指令旨在压制他们对总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的批评</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 12:16:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/reservists-in-elite-iaf-units-say-ordered-to-steer-clear-during-netanyahu-visit/0000018c-5de2-dbd5-a39c-fff308230000</guid></item><item><title>以色列空军军官在美国发生肇事逃逸事件中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-air-force-officer-killed-in-a-hit-and-run-accident-in-the-u-s/0000018c-5d92-de43-affd-fd929fc40000</link><description>40 岁的叶霍纳坦·纳洪 (Yehonatan Nahon) 在西雅图雷德蒙德社区被一辆汽车驶上人行道撞倒，受重伤。司机逃离现场，纳洪因伤重不治身亡</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 11:05:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-air-force-officer-killed-in-a-hit-and-run-accident-in-the-u-s/0000018c-5d92-de43-affd-fd929fc40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院讨论允许两名母亲列入孩子出生证明的请愿书</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-high-court-discusses-allowing-two-mothers-to-be-listed-on-a-birth-certificate/0000018c-5d6d-d04c-a5ff-7fed96080000</link><description>目前，以色列内政部从孩子的出生证明中删除了一名非亲生母亲的名字。该请愿书已等待八年，旨在实现同性伴侣子女的平等地位</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 10:30:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-high-court-discusses-allowing-two-mothers-to-be-listed-on-a-birth-certificate/0000018c-5d6d-d04c-a5ff-7fed96080000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵看到在约旦河西岸向巴勒斯坦人开枪，然后在地面上再次向他开枪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-seen-shooting-palestinian-in-west-bank-then-shooting-him-again/0000018c-5d52-d0ec-afbe-df72bc0b0000</link><description>一名 25 岁男子在纳布卢斯附近中枪受伤后被枪杀，以色列国防军已对士兵非法射击展开调查</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 09:52:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-seen-shooting-palestinian-in-west-bank-then-shooting-him-again/0000018c-5d52-d0ec-afbe-df72bc0b0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦囚犯俱乐部负责人称，以色列拘留了 153 名加沙妇女，其中一些还带着孩子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-detained-153-gazan-women-some-with-babies-says-palestinian-prisoners-club-head/0000018c-5d37-d03f-af9f-7d772cdf0000</link><description>尽管以色列国防军拘留加沙男子的照片广为人知且颇具争议，但对这些妇女的逮捕却“没有受到关注”</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 09:50:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-detained-153-gazan-women-some-with-babies-says-palestinian-prisoners-club-head/0000018c-5d37-d03f-af9f-7d772cdf0000</guid></item><item><title>也门胡塞武装声称在红海袭击了前往以色列的挪威油轮</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/yemens-houthis-claim-attack-on-norwegian-oil-tanker-en-route-to-israel-in-the-red-sea/0000018c-5d0e-d0ec-afbe-df2e167c0000</link><description>胡塞武装发誓要攻击任何开往以色列港口的船只，直到援助抵达加沙为止。船东表示STRINDA油轮已在前往意大利的途中</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 09:35:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/yemens-houthis-claim-attack-on-norwegian-oil-tanker-en-route-to-israel-in-the-red-sea/0000018c-5d0e-d0ec-afbe-df2e167c0000</guid></item></channel></rss>